text: Quaid-e-Azam Residency (), also known as Ziarat Residency, is located in Ziarat, Balochistan, Pakistan. It is where Quaid-e-Azam, Muhammad Ali Jinnah spent the last two months and ten days of his life. Category:1892 establishments Category:National symbols of Pakistan Category:Museums in Pakistan
title: Quaid-e-Azam Residency
